<p>The meetings are free and open to the public and once you’ve registered, you will receive a confirmation email that includes the precise location of the meeting. The meetings will start with a short introduction to update you on the progress made so far in the negotiations and will be followed by a Q&A session.</p>

<p>Visit our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/living-in-italy">Living in Italy guide</a> for practical information, such as how to register as a resident. You can receive email alerts whenever the guide is updated by <a href="https://www.gov.uk/email-signup/?topic=/world/living-in-italy">signing up here</a>.</p>

