<p>For questions concerning your rights as a British citizen in Italy <a rel="external" href="https://www.contact-embassy.service.gov.uk/?country=Italy&post=British%20Embassy%20Rome">contact us</a>.</p>

<p>If you have any suggestions for other towns and places that could host our citizens outreach meetings, please email <a href="mailto:uknationals.initaly@fco.gov.uk">uknationals.initaly@fco.gov.uk</a>.</p>

